<L>__{exterior field. devon. dusk.}
<A>__{suddenly, we are back in the village in devon, in the fold of the valley. dusk light. a figure approaches, silhouetted against the setting sun. mrs. naracott gathers the harvest, then notices as the figure makes its way up the road to the farm. a man in uniform. on a magnificent horse. mrs. narracott meets them at the gate and we can finally see them clearly albert and joey. albert dismounts and removes his cap. an instant later, mrs. narracott is hugging him for all that her life is worth.}
